<br>
Stormygale's treatments had come to an end, although Saphron was the only person who knew it. With the help of the shaman Kyusz, and the willingness (or was it willfulness?) and dedication of the druidess, the treatments had been a success.<br>
<br>
Today would begin the recuperation phase. Stormygale would need to be relatively careful with her back, but she could resume some normal adventuring - slowly, but surely. She would not even <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>have</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> to remain in the tree, but Saphron hoped she would.<br>
<br>
