<br>
&quot;My fear is more of what will come out of this.  Seeking this person out will only do more harm.  They are waiting for you Stormygale.&quot;  Kandiya's eyes darkened and her voice got softer.  &quot;You must make her come to you......&quot;<br>
<br>
